sentiment_score_definition: x <= -0.35: Bearish; -0.35 < x <= -0.15: Somewhat-Bearish; -0.15 < x < 0.15: Neutral; 0.15 <= x < 0.35: Somewhat_Bullish; x >= 0.35: Bullish
relevance_score_definition: 0 < x <= 1, with a higher score indicating higher relevance.

feed.title: Axiom Intelligence Acquisition Corp 1 SEC 10-Q Report
feed.summary: Axiom Intelligence Acquisition Corp 1 (AXIN), a blank check company targeting the European infrastructure industry, has released its Form 10-Q report for Q3 2025. The report details financial performance including $1.9 million in net income and $0.07 net income per share for the quarter, largely from interest on its Trust Account. AXIN completed its IPO on June 20, 2025, raising $200 million for its Trust Account, and aims to complete a business combination by June 20, 2027.
